    "abstract": "<jats:title>ABSTRACT</jats:title>\n                <jats:p>The lockdown due to coronavirus pandemic may exacerbate depressive symptoms, experts argue. Here we report that students, a high-risk category for mental disorders, report on average worse depressive symptoms than six months before isolation. The prospective data reported herein should alert clinician of a possible aggravation as well as new-onsets of depressive symptoms in students.</jats:p>",
